t-size:12pt">In the survey, 60% of those asked described use of spending data as ‘low’ or ‘very low’ with another 30% not knowing.  </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">The highest </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">use </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">was 5357 pageviews in a 24 month period (a County Council) and the lowest 210 pageviews in a 26 month period (a District Council).  </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">The</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt"> emerging picture of low use is supported by other research.</span><a name="_ftnref13"></a><a href="#_ftn13">[13]</a><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">This can be compared with visits to other sites (note visits and page views are different</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt"> and</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt"> the table</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt"> is indicative only)</span><a name="_ftnref14"></a><a href="#_ftn14">[14]</a><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt"> </span></p><div style="text-align:center"><table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="border-collapse:collapse; margin:0 auto"><tr><td style="border-bottom-color:#000000; border-bottom-style:solid; border-bottom-width:0.5pt; border-left-color:#000000; border-left-style:solid; border-left-width:0.5pt; border-right-color:#000000; border-right-style:solid; border-right-width:0.5pt; border-top-color:#000000; border-top-style:solid; border-top-width:0.5pt; padding-left:5.4pt; padding-right:5.4pt; vertical-align:top; width:103.5pt"><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 17.85pt; text-indent:-17.85pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">Site</span></p></td><td style="border-bottom-color:#000000; border-bottom-style:solid; border-bottom-width:0.5pt; border-left-color:#000000; bo